## Other console class options

__Some of these options may not work in VS Code console. Please run this code in Visual Studio.__

#!csharp

// Makes a beep sound.
Console.Beep();

// Clears the console. Might cause an error in VS Code.
Console.Clear();

// This property returns true if the caps lock is on, otherwise false.
Console.WriteLine(Console.CapsLock);

// Gets or sets the visibility of the cursor.
Console.WriteLine(Console.CursorVisible);
Console.CursorVisible = false;

// Gets a value indicating the the NUM Lock is on or off.
Console.WriteLine(Console.NumberLock);
